      <description>&lt;p&gt;XFCE desktop environment requires fewer system resources, making it ideal for running on older hardware or low-powered machines.
It runs smoothly on systems with as little as 512MB of RAM, making it an excellent option for lightweight laptops, netbooks, and desktops.



